:64},{"id":"recfnPAYdMtoGqpUG","ref":"Eph.6.5","text":"Servants, be obedient to them that are your masters according to the flesh, with fear and trembling, in singleness of your heart, as unto Christ;","year":64},{"id":"recYoSLwfcc5PzCUk","ref":"Eph.6.6","text":"Not with eyeservice, as menpleasers; but as the servants of Christ, doing the will of God from the heart;","year":64},{"id":"rec2lyrmvUnPI7vRA","ref":"Eph.6.7","text":"With good will doing service, as to the Lord, and not to men:","year":64},{"id":"recaW1QC4gdR46eHr","ref":"Eph.6.8","text":"Knowing that whatsoever good thing any man doeth, the same shall he receive of the Lord, whether he be bond or free.","year":64}]}
